# Include Directory

This directory is reserved for project-wide headers that do not naturally belong
to one library under `lib/`.

Most interfaces should stay close to their owner module:

- display interfaces under `lib/Display`;
- mount interfaces under `lib/Mount`;
- input interfaces under `lib/Input`;
- telescope/config interfaces under `lib/Telescope`;
- system helpers under `lib/System`.

Use this directory only for truly shared contracts that are used across multiple
independent modules. Avoid turning it into a dumping ground for global state.
